captions.text: I'm very impressed. It's great to see that we have such a high level.
"Brizze" (the winner) had, besides the skills and all the tricks he showed...
a swagger upon him. He was an entertainer and he did not only use his skills...
with the ball, but also just his personal appearance, which led to the verdict...
of "Brizze" winning the final two votes against one.

title: Freestyle football competition - Red Bull Street Style Denmark
